零五以上。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/110%2c%e5%8e%9f%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c39%2c20211014%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,110,原交易,39,20211014,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"原交易","JNO":"39","JDATE":"20211014","JTITLE":"公共危險"}